text: O, My Darling Clementine is a 1943 American musical movie directed by Frank McDonald and stars Roy Acuff, Isabel Randolph, Harry Cheshire, Frank Albertson, Lorna Gray, Irene Ryan, Edwin Stanley, Emmett Vogan. It was distributed by Republic Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1943 musical movies Category:American musical movies Category:Movies directed by Frank McDonald
